Audi to Create 10,000 Jobs Globally Through 2020, Stadler Says

-- B y   M a r i a j o s e   V e r a
-- 
2011-05-12T08:00:00Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-12/audi-to-create-10-000-jobs-globally-through-2020-stadler-says.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Audi luxury-car
division plans to create 10,000 jobs globally through 2020,
Chief Executive Officer Rupert Stadler said today, according to
the prepared speech for the company’s shareholder meeting in
Neckarsulm,  Germany . Audi expects “further growth” beyond 2015,
Stadler added.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Mariajose Vera in Munich at 
 mvera1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at   acullen8@bloomberg.net . 